race.description: Marine One Yearlings 2026 Westspeed Platinum Plt
race.comment: The 2YO's now and ACE QUEEN SUITED (10) looks to right the wrongs of her debut. She jumped the favourite there and finished off strongly, though she couldn't reel in the winner, beaten 0.4L. The inside draw suits better now and Chris Parnham hops in the saddle. Can turn the tables. HE'S A MACHINO (6) has won both trials coming into this and gets Pike in the saddle for his debut. He showed good fight in his latest outing to get the job done and there's plenty to like. Draw is the query, but he looks to have good ability. RED LARK (1) was plain fresh but got the job done last start, beaten ACE QUEEN SUITED in the process. Likely to be in the second half once again, but his race experience may be the difference once again. BOB THE BAKER (5) trialled behind a smart one most recently and has to be included with CJP taking the ride. UNTAMED STARE (12) was solid in her only trial at Lark Hill and can be finishing strongly.
